    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You quickly brush off a hostile effect in order to keep the show going, deflecting any harm back onto your enemies. You immediately regain Xd4 + X hit points (X = your Genjutsu ability modifier) and can clear yourself of all instances of one condition of your choice that you are suffering from.</p><p>Then, one hostile creature within range must make a Charisma saving throw, taking the result of your healing as psychic damage that ignores resistance and being Dazed on a failure, or half as much and no additional effects on a success.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost by 3 and the die step by 1.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
